## Blog Images

The blog service handles images with a fallback system:

1. **Contentful asset** — If the post has a `featuredImage` in Contentful, use its CDN URL
2. **Deterministic placeholder** — If no asset, use `getStableImage(id)` which maps the entry ID to one of 10 placeholder images (`/images/blog-medspa-01.jpg` through `blog-medspa-10.jpg`)

This ensures:

- Same post always gets the same placeholder
- Adding new posts doesn't shuffle existing placeholder assignments

